data.description: SPECIAL HOLIDAY BONUS OFFER! Seller offering a $10,000 closing cost credit on acceptable full price offer received by December 31, 2023! Welcome to Colorado living at its best! Lovely 2 story home is in the perfect location. Tucked away, but easily accessible from I-25 in The Meadows community in Castle Rock, it is close to so many great, local amenities. As you enter the home from the covered front porch, you are greeted by warm toned, trowel finish walls, hardwood flooring & a ton of natural light. The front living & formal dining areas are perfect for entertaining family & friends. Main level office is nestled away from the main living area for a quiet work space. The open kitchen & great room is warm & cozy with a gas fireplace, eating nook & lots of windows. The kitchen has a large center island, beautiful slab granite countertops, stainless steel appliances & double oven range. You will enjoy the large walk-in pantry & expanse of counter prep space. Also on the main level is a powder bath & wonderful mud room area right off of the garage entry. Head on up to the upper level of this home & you will find a large, private, primary bedroom suite w/ beautiful double vanity, huge walk-in shower & fantastic walk-in closet. Additionally on the upper level is a very large loft area great for a kids lounge, additional office or workout space or living area. Rounding out the upper level are 3 additional bedrooms, a large full bath & convenient laundry room. The partial basement is ready for your personal finishes & includes a crawl space storage area, sump pump & radon mitigation. You will have plenty of space for vehicles or toys in the 3 car attached garage. The lovely tiered backyard has great space for play and entertaining. New water heat er, newer roof with Class 4 shingles (2017). Easy access to the Ridgeline Trail Space, neighborhood trails & beautiful downtown Castle Rock. Schedule a viewing today!
